node.text: I’m very good at competing and I am ready to compete for EVERY Californian. Democrat, Independent, Republican - EVERYONE. Join me. Link in bio.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caitlyn Jenner on August 19, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: My heart aches for those that have lost everything in these fires. We are Californians, we are strong, and we will rebuild. As governor I will restore hope in our government and be one with the people. #californiastrong

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caitlyn Jenner on August 19, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people sitting and indoor.

node.text: We are facing devastating fires largely due to policy failures and cuts to our fire budget. I am on the ground at this disaster zone learning first hand what needs to be done to contain and manage our fires.

node.text: Meeting with local business innovators discussing the crippling regulations that small businesses face in CA. I will cut regulations, taxes, and encourage small biz growth.

node.text:
Met with @logcabinoc to talk about freedom, liberty, and kicking Gavin Newsom the hell out of office!

REMINDER: The deadline for counties to send mail-in ballots to all registered voters is this Monday. Go vote!

node.text: So much fun meeting voters at cars and coffee today in Orange County! We are full speed ahead and will shake as many hands and hear as many stories as possible in every corner of the state!

node.text: Visited the California / Mexico border to meet with the brave men and woman protecting our border. I will secure the border, finish the wall, and advocate for legal immigration! Can you believe our current governor has never even been here?  Vote him out on September 14!

node.text: As governor I will use state funds to close the gaps in our wall. Fun fact: Gavin Newsom has never even been to the border. Great day meeting with border patrol agents.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caitlyn Jenner in Venice Beach. May be an image of 4 people, people standing and outdoors.

node.text: Proud to work and meet with the Venice Neighborhood association. They truly are on the front lines of battling the homeless crisis in their community. As governor I will be with you to help the homeless and your community.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Caitlyn Jenner on August 12, 2021. May be an image of one or more people, people standing and indoor.

node.text: Great evening with supporters! My favorite part of this campaign is meeting with the voters
